2. COMPARATIVE ALGORITHMS (THIRD-PARTY)
The implementations of "Backtracking" and "Warnsdorff's Heuristic" 
included in this suite are provided solely for comparative 
benchmarking purposes. They are standard algorithmic 
implementations and their conceptual authorship belongs to their 
respective historical creators.

3. RESTRICTIONS
This entire suite is provided to reviewers and researchers for 
evaluation purposes only. Unauthorized copying, distribution, or 
use of the "Nemertea" logic for publication or commercial ends 
is strictly prohibited until the official publication of the 
associated research paper.

4. FUTURE OPEN SOURCE COMMITMENT
Upon acceptance and publication of the research, the author 
commits to re-licensing this entire suite under an Open Source 
initiative (e.g., MIT or GNU GPL) to foster multilateral 
scientific collaboration.